# CAGE: Causality-Aware Gene Evaluator

CAGE prioritizes candidate genes integrating causality, environment-awareness,
multi-layer validation, and external cohort replication.

[![Python 3.10+](https://img.shields.io/badge/python-3.10%2B-blue.svg)](#requirements)
[![License: MIT](https://img.shields.io/badge/license-MIT-green.svg)](LICENSE)
[![NumPy-only](https://img.shields.io/badge/backend-pure%20NumPy-orange.svg)](#design-philosophy)

