### Running All Sub-Steps at Once

```bash
python -m cage.step8_external_validation_and_release all \
  --gse GSE23400 GSE38129 GSE161533 GSE20347 GSE53624 GSE53625 \
  --step5-dir outputs/step5_cdps \
  --step6-dir outputs/step6_validation \
  --step4-dir outputs/step4_deep_model \
  --step7-dir outputs/final_package \
  --output-dir outputs/step8 \
  --run-model \
  --build-reviewer-bundle \
  --seed 2026
```

This writes to `outputs/step8/geo_prepared/`, `outputs/step8/geo_validation/`,
`outputs/step8/agilent_validation/`, and `outputs/step8/release/` respectively.

